                            <comment id="17212868" author="ifesdjeen" created="Tue, 13 Oct 2020 06:39:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dcapwell&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dcapwell&quot;&gt;dcapwell&lt;/a&gt; it looks like it got merged away while I was rebasing. Turned out that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=marcuse&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;marcuse&quot;&gt;marcuse&lt;/a&gt; has made the same change in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/4d173e0a3f97b68b2ce0fb72befe2912efd31102#diff-321b52220c5bd0aaadf275a845143eb208c889c2696ba0d48a5fc880551131d8L266&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;this patch&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;d still say it&apos;s useful to merge the test in.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
